[15px] font-light text-[var(--color-text)] hover:text-[var(--color-muted)] transition-colors duration-150\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></div></div></nav><div class=\"mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-[var(--color-border)] flex gap-5 flex-shrink-0\"><a href=\"https://instagram.com/kvrn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"text-[11px] tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-[var(--color-muted)] hover:text-[var(--color-text)] transition-colors\">Instagram</a></div></div><div class=\"fixed inset-0 z-[300] transition-all duration-300 bg-transparent pointer-events-none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div role=\"dialog\" aria-modal=\"true\" aria-label=\"Shopping bag\" class=\"fixed top-0 right-0 bottom-0 z-[400] w-full max-w-[400px] bg-[var(--color-bg)] flex flex-col transition-transform duration-[550ms] ease-[cubic-bezier(0.25,0.46,0.45,0.94)] translate-x-full\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-5 border-b border-[var(--color-border)]\"><h2 class=\"text-[11px] font-light tracking-[0.14em] uppercase\">Bag</h2><button aria-label=\"Close bag\" class=\"p-2 -mr-2 opacity-40 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity\"><svg width=\"18\" height=\"18\" viewBox=\"0 0 18 18\" fill=\"none\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M3 3l12 12M15 3L3 15\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"></path></svg></button></div><div class=\"flex-1 overflow-y-auto scrollbar-thin\"><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center justify-center h-full px-6 text-center gap-5\"><p class=\"text-[14px] font-light text-[var(--color-muted)]\">Your bag is empty.</p><a href=\"/shop\"><button aria-busy=\"false\" class=\"relative inline-flex items-center justify-center font-body font-light tracking-widest uppercase transition-all duration-150 ease-out select-none whitespace-nowrap -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent bg-transparent text-kvrn-text border border-kvrn-text hover:bg-kvrn-text hover:text-kvrn-bg active:bg-[#333333] disabled:opacity-40 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:pointer-events-none h-10 px-5 text-[11px]\"><span class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">Browse collection</span></button></a></div></div></div><main id=\"main-content\"><div class=\"pt-[56px]\" id=\"size-guide\"><div class=\"container-kvrn section-padding max-w-3xl\"><nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\" class=\"mb-10\"><ol class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-[11px] text-kvrn-muted tracking-wide\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-kvrn-text transition-colors\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li aria-hidden=\"true\">·</li><li><a class=\"hover:text-kvrn-text transition-colors\" href=\"/support/faq\">Support</a></li><li aria-hidden=\"true\">·</li><li class=\"text-kvrn-text\" aria-current=\"page\">Size Guide</li></ol></nav><h1 class=\"font-display font-light text-[40px] md:text-[56px] leading-none tracking-tighter mb-6\">Size Guide</h1><div class=\"border border-kvrn-border p-5 md:p-7 mb-14 bg-kvrn-bg-raised\"><p class=\"label-11 mb-3\">How KVRN fits</p><p class=\"text-[14px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed mb-3\">KVRN is designed to be oversized. The silhouette is deliberate — wide through the chest and shoulders, long in the body, with a structured hood that sits high.</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-[14px] text-kvrn-muted\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-2 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-kvrn-muted\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span><strong class=\"font-light text-kvrn-text\">Intended fit:</strong> Buy your normal size for the full oversized silhouette.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-2 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-kvrn-muted\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span><strong class=\"font-light text-kvrn-text\">Cleaner look:</strong> Size down one for a slightly more structured oversized shape.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-2 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-kvrn-muted\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span><strong class=\"font-light text-kvrn-text\">Between sizes:</strong> Size down.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-3\"><span class=\"flex-shrink-0 mt-2 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-kvrn-muted\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span><strong class=\"font-light text-kvrn-text\">Unsure?</strong> Email <a href=\"mailto:hello@kvrn.com\" class=\"text-kvrn-text underline underline-offset-2\">hello@kvrn.com</a> with your height and usual size — we&#x27;ll advise directly.</span></li></ul></div><section class=\"mb-14\" aria-labelledby=\"measure-heading\"><h2 id=\"measure-heading\" class=\"label-11 mb-6\">How to measure</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-5\"><div class=\"border-l-2 border-kvrn-border pl-4\"><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-kvrn-text mb-1\">Chest</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\">Measure around the fullest part of your chest, keeping the tape parallel to the floor. Add 6–10cm for our intended oversized fit.</p></div><div class=\"border-l-2 border-kvrn-border pl-4\"><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-kvrn-text mb-1\">Body length</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\">Measured from the centre back neck point to the finished hem. All measurements are taken flat on the garment.</p></div><div class=\"border-l-2 border-kvrn-border pl-4\"><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-kvrn-text mb-1\">Sleeve</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\">Measured from the top of the shoulder seam to the finished cuff, with the arm extended flat.</p></div><div class=\"border-l-2 border-kvrn-border pl-4\"><p class=\"text-[13px] font-light text-kvrn-text mb-1\">Waist (sweatpants)</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted leading-relaxed\">Measured flat across the waistband × 2. The elastic waistband stretches — these measurements reflect the relaxed state.</p></div></div><p class=\"text-[12px] text-kvrn-muted mt-4\">All measurements in centimetres, taken flat. Manufacturing tolerance: ±1.5cm.</p></section><section class=\"mb-14\" aria-labelledby=\"hoodie-table-heading\"><h2 id=\"hoodie-table-heading\" class=\"label-11 mb-6\">KVRN Heavyweight Hoodie — Garment Measurements (cm)</h2><div class=\"overflow-x-auto\"><table class=\"w-full text-[13px]\" aria-label=\"Hoodie size measurements\"><thead><tr class=\"border-b border-kvrn-border\"><th class=\"text-left py-3 pr-6 font-light label-11\">Size</th><th class=\"text-left py-3 pr-6 font-light label-11\">Chest</th><th class=\"text-left py-3 pr-6 font-light label-11\">Body length</th><th class=\"text-left py-3 pr-6 font-light label-11\">Sleeve</th><th class=\"text-left py-3 pr-6 font-light label-11\">Shoulder</th></tr></thead><tbody class=\"divide-y divide-kvrn-border\"><tr class=\"hover:bg-kvrn-bg-raised transition-colors\"><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 font-light text-kvrn-text\">XS</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">60</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">72</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">63</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">52</td></tr><tr class=\"hover:bg-kvrn-bg-raised transition-colors\"><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 font-light text-kvrn-text\">S</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">64</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">74</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">64</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">54</td></tr><tr class=\"hover:bg-kvrn-bg-raised transition-colors\"><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 font-light text-kvrn-text\">M</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">68</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">76</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">65</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">56</td></tr><tr class=\"hover:bg-kvrn-bg-raised transition-colors\"><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 font-light text-kvrn-text\">L</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">72</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">78</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">66</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">58</td></tr><tr class=\"hover:bg-kvrn-bg-raised transition-colors\"><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 font-light text-kvrn-text\">XL</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">76</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">80</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">67</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">60</td></tr><tr class=\"hover:bg-kvrn-bg-raised transition-colors\"><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 font-light text-kvrn-text\">XXL</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">80</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">82</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">68</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">62</td></tr></tbody></table></div><a class=\"inline-block mt-5 text-[13px] text-kvrn-muted hover:text-kvrn-text transition-colors underline underline-offset-2\" href=\"/products/kvrn-heavyweight-hoodie\">Shop the Hoodie →</a></section><section class=\"mb-14\" aria-labelledby=\"sweatpants-table-heading\"><h2 id=\"sweatpants-table-heading\" class=\"label-11 mb-6\">KVRN Heavyweight Sweatpants — Garment Measurements (cm)</h2><div class=\"overflow-x-auto\"><table class=\"w-full text-[13px]\" aria-label=\"Sweatpants size measurements\"><thead><tr class=\"border-b border-kvrn-border\"><th class=\"text-left py-3 pr-6 font-light label-11\">Size</th><th class=\"text-left py-3 pr-6 font-light label-11\">Waist (relaxed)</th><th class=\"text-left py-3 pr-6 font-light label-11\">Hip</th><th class=\"text-left py-3 pr-6 font-light label-11\">Inseam</th><th class=\"text-left py-3 pr-6 font-light label-11\">Leg opening</th></tr></thead><tbody class=\"divide-y divide-kvrn-border\"><tr class=\"hover:bg-kvrn-bg-raised transition-colors\"><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 font-light text-kvrn-text\">XS</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">64</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">90</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">74</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">22</td></tr><tr class=\"hover:bg-kvrn-bg-raised transition-colors\"><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 font-light text-kvrn-text\">S</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">68</td><td class=\"py-3 pr-6 text-kvrn-muted\">94</td><td class=\"p